Report about canids: Canids are the dog-like carnivores. Using unix commands, there are 160 unique species in 58 genera. Cormocyon copei has the longest fossil record

Report about bats: These are data for the microchiroptera, essentially nocturnal bats. Note here, it seems that there’s been some reclassification since I last learned about this group.

Using unix commands, there are 35 unique species in 19 genera.

Rhinolophus grivensis has the longest fossil record.
